{
  "texts": [
    "PolitiFact fact-checkers rely on evidence from official records and verified data to assess the truthfulness of claims.",
    "4 In the context of the Vote frame, claims often reference specific congressional bills.",
    "To evaluate our system, we constructed an evaluation dataset by extracting all PolitiFact fact-checks made before April 2022 that involve claims related to the Vote frame and reference at least one congressional bill.",
    "After manual verification, we collected 79 fact-checks, along with their corresponding bills, to form the evaluation set.",
    "Congress member identification."
  ]
}